overview:
MP3ShopsCompare.com is where you can find the cheapest MP3s by comparing prices across all different MP3 sites without having to spend all your money on iTunes! Everyone should be able to buy MP3s at a fair price while buying it legally, which is our objective.

Because of iTunes, we have so many people paying a premium for tracks that should be far cheaper, which is why so many people choose to look for illegal music downloads. So instead of putting yourself at risk by illegal downloading, we put together the cheapest MP3 sites out there, complete with reviews that will guide you to the best sites. You can contact us through the site or through email for thoughts, comments or suggestions in order to make the site better and easier for you to use
